 about these for quite a while, and this is what we've come up with:<br><br>1. We may be moving the forums from EZboards over to PHP or another locall hosted forum script. This would mean having to bring over a lot of posts and losing all of the current titles and stuff, but we'll have a lot more control over the boards, and no advertising or donation hassles.<br><br>2. We will be banning a few people we've been keeping track of lately. They don't add anything to the boards, and generally make the whole community look bad. A list will be posted later.<br><br>3. Graffe is stepping down from running the site. We've contacted Grimstaff, and he said he'll be happy to take over. Everyone welcome him to the new job =)<br><br>4. We will be removing the spell section from the main site, it will redirect you to the Castersrealm spell list, which is much more up to date and accurate.<br><br>5. Frozboz is a new Moderator of General Discussion. His powers are in General Discussion only, to help with the influx of posts recently. Welcome Froz =)<br><br>6. We're going to be a lot more strict on post placement. If a post talks about balance at all, it will be moved to Class Balance. If a thread contains an form of profanity, it will be moved to Rants. This is to keep General clean and informative.<br><br>Thanks for the time.<br><br> <p><P align=center>Samadhi, 60<sup>th</sup> Sorcerer<BR><A href="http://web.icq.com/wwp?Uin=36490487"> ICQ #</A> | <A href="http://www.drow.org">BotS</A> | <A href="mailto:samadhi@graffe.com?subject=Hi, my name is Bob, and I'm an alcoholic.">E-mail</A></P></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufeynanthewizard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FeynantheWizard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/1/02 12:49:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationf